	* tests/diff-po:
	* tests/init-po:
	* tests/validate/1:
	* tests/validate/4:
	* tests/diff-po-0.po:
	* tests/diff-po-1.po: Add more tests.
	* gnun-diff-po.in: Accept a directory name as the second FILE
	argument.
	* gnun-merge-preconverted.in: Add the `--disable-diffs'
	option.
	* gnun-diff-po.in:
	* gnun-init-po.in:
	* gnun-merge-preconverted.in:
	* gnun-preconvert.in:
	* gnun-report.in:
