	(generic.LANG.html): Remove node.
	(Runtime Variables) <VCS=yes>: Update description.
	(Files and Directories): Exclude *.m4 and
	server/gnun/generic.*.html files from diagram.
	* AUTHORS:
	* NEWS: Update.
	* README: Minor clarifications.

